---
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<html lang="pt-BR">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<link rel="icon" href="/favicon.ico" />
		<meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
		<title>Projeto Teste — Laboratório de IA</title>
	</head>
	<body>
		<header>
			<div class="logo">IA Lab</div>
			<nav>
				<a href="#features">Recursos</a>
				<a href="#status">Status</a>
			</nav>
		</header>

		<section class="hero">
			<span class="badge">⚡ Rodando na borda da Cloudflare</span>
			<h1>Laboratório de <span>IA e ferramentas experimentais</span></h1>
			<p class="subtitle">
				Frontend em Astro + Tailwind e uma API em Python (Cloudflare Workers)
				para prototipar ideias direto na borda, com custo zero no plano free.
			</p>
			<div class="cta">
				<a href="#features" class="btn btn-primary">Ver a stack</a>
				<a href="#status" class="btn btn-secondary">Status do ambiente</a>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="features" id="features">
			<div class="card">
				<div class="icon">🚀</div>
				<h3>Astro + Tailwind</h3>
				<p>Site estático gerado no build, servido como assets — grátis e ilimitado no plano free.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="card">
				<div class="icon">🐍</div>
				<h3>Python Worker</h3>
				<p>API em <code>/api/*</code> rodando Python nativo (Pyodide) num Worker separado, same-origin.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="card">
				<div class="icon">🤖</div>
				<h3>Automação</h3>
				<p>Setup, deploy e ajustes de arquitetura conduzidos ponta a ponta com o Claude Code.</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<footer id="status">
			Ambiente no ar — pronto para o próximo passo 🚀
		</footer>

		<style>
			:root {
				--bg: #0f1117;
				--bg-alt: #161925;
				--text: #f4f4f5;
				--text-muted: #a1a1aa;
				--accent: #6366f1;
				--accent-light: #818cf8;
			}
			* { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
			body {
				font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, sans-serif;
				background: var(--bg);
				color: var(--text);
				line-height: 1.6;
			}
			header {
				display: flex;
				align-items: center;
				justify-content: space-between;
				padding: 24px 8%;
				border-bottom: 1px solid #232635;
			}
			.logo {
				font-weight: 700;
				font-size: 1.25rem;
				color: var(--accent-light);
			}
			nav a {
				color: var(--text-muted);
				text-decoration: none;
				margin-left: 32px;
				font-size: 0.95rem;
				transition: color 0.2s;
			}
			nav a:hover { color: var(--text); }
			.hero {
				text-align: center;
				padding: 120px 8% 100px;
				background: radial-gradient(circle at top, var(--bg-alt), var(--bg));
			}
			.badge {
				display: inline-block;
				background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.15);
				color: var(--accent-light);
				padding: 6px 16px;
				border-radius: 999px;
				font-size: 0.85rem;
				margin-bottom: 24px;
			}
			h1 {
				font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 3.6rem);
				font-weight: 800;
				max-width: 800px;
				margin: 0 auto 20px;
			}
			h1 span { color: var(--accent-light); }
			.subtitle {
				color: var(--text-muted);
				font-size: 1.15rem;
				max-width: 560px;
				margin: 0 auto 36px;
			}
			.cta {
				display: inline-flex;
				gap: 16px;
			}
			.btn {
				padding: 14px 28px;
				border-radius: 8px;
				font-weight: 600;
				text-decoration: none;
				font-size: 0.95rem;
				transition: transform 0.15s, opacity 0.15s;
			}
			.btn:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); }
			.btn-primary {
				background: var(--accent);
				color: white;
			}
			.btn-secondary {
				background: transparent;
				color: var(--text);
				border: 1px solid #33364a;
			}
			.features {
				display: grid;
				grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
				gap: 24px;
				padding: 0 8% 100px;
				max-width: 1100px;
				margin: 0 auto;
			}
			.card {
				background: var(--bg-alt);
				border: 1px solid #232635;
				border-radius: 12px;
				padding: 28px;
			}
			.card .icon {
				font-size: 1.8rem;
				margin-bottom: 12px;
			}
			.card h3 {
				font-size: 1.1rem;
				margin-bottom: 8px;
			}
			.card p {
				color: var(--text-muted);
				font-size: 0.95rem;
			}
			.card code {
				background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
				padding: 2px 6px;
				border-radius: 4px;
				font-size: 0.85em;
			}
			footer {
				text-align: center;
				padding: 32px;
				color: var(--text-muted);
				font-size: 0.85rem;
				border-top: 1px solid #232635;
			}
		</style>
	</body>
</html>
